                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div>
                <div class="sticky top-40">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                        <h1 class="text-4xl font-black text-[#27334B]">Product Name</h1>
                        <button class="text-gray-400 hover:text-red-500">
                            <svg class="w-7 h-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"></path></svg>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center mt-2">
                        <span class="text-yellow-400">★★★★☆</span>
                        <span class="ml-2 text-gray-500 text-sm">(22)</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="mt-4 font-black text-3xl text-[#27334B]">₱ 1,100</p>

                    <div class="mt-6">
                        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-700">Select Type:</p>
                        <div class="flex gap-4 mt-2">
                            <button class="px-6 py-2 bg-[#5977AF] text-white font-semibold rounded-full">Pre-made</button>
                            <button class="px-6 py-2 bg-[#5977AF] text-white font-semibold rounded-full">Custom</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-6">
                        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-700">Quantity:</p>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mt-2">
                            <button class="h-10 w-10 border rounded-full font-bold text-lg">-</button>
                            <span class="font-bold text-lg">1</span>
                            <button class="h-10 w-10 border rounded-full font-bold text-lg">+</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-6">
                        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-700">Add-ons:</p>
                        <div class="flex gap-4 mt-2">
                            <button class="px-6 py-2 bg-[#5977AF] text-white font-semibold rounded-full">Card</button>
                            <button class="px-6 py-2 bg-[#5977AF] text-white font-semibold rounded-full">Vase</button>
                            <button class="px-6 py-2 bg-[#5977AF] text-white font-semibold rounded-full">Treats</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                        <button class="w-full py-3 bg-[#5977AF] text-white font-bold rounded-full">Add To Cart</button>
                        <button class="w-full py-3 bg-[#5977AF] text-white font-bold rounded-full">Buy Now</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section class="bg-[#E0F1FF] py-16">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-[#27334B] mb-8">Related Products</h2>
            <div id="related-products-scroll" class="flex space-x-6 pb-4 overflow-x-auto [scrollbar-width:none] [&::-webkit-scrollbar]:hidden">
                <div class="flex-none w-72 h-48 bg-[#DFEDF9] rounded-lg shadow-md relative overflow-hidden group"></div>
                <div class="flex-none w-72 h-48 bg-[#DFEDF9] rounded-lg shadow-md relative overflow-hidden group"></div>
                <div class="flex-none w-72 h-48 bg-[#DFEDF9] rounded-lg shadow-md relative overflow-hidden group"></div>
